OL,3,CFootball fan threw glass bottle at
OL,4,Cpolice officer's face
OL,6,FA football fan who threw a glass
OL,7,Fbottle at a police officer's face has
OL,8,Fbeen banned from attending another
OL,9,Fmatch for five years.
OL,11,FThe "shocking" incident happened
OL,12,Fshortly before the Merseyside derby
OL,13,Fgame at Anfield, Liverpool, on 21
OL,14,FOctober 2023.
OL,16,FBen O'Meara was walking along 97th
OL,17,FAvenue with a group of Everton
OL,18,Fsupporters, when he picked up a bottle
OL,19,Fand launched it at an officer, causing
OL,20,Fa deep cut to his face and mouth.
