OL,6,FThe 25-year-old, from Prescot,
OL,7,FMerseyside, was identified after
OL,8,Fofficers reviewed CCTV, and he was
OL,9,Flater arrested and charged with
OL,10,Fassault.
OL,12,FO'Meara, who appeared before South
OL,13,FSefton Magistrates Court, pleaded
OL,14,Fguilty and was issued a 26-week
OL,15,Fimprisonment, suspended for 18 months,
OL,16,Fand a five-year banning order.
OL,18,FHe was issued 20 days rehabilitation,
OL,19,F200 hours unpaid work and told to pay
OL,20,F#500 compensation to the victim.
